lead_paragraph: Rain dampened the enthusiasm of a festive Boxing Day crowd but Australia were content to knock over Pakistan's top order and leave the tourists 142 for four on day one of the second test in Melbourne on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Australia Hold Edge After Rain Dampens Boxing Day Cheer
